      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Slow Chess</b>\n</p><p><b>Slow Chess</b>, (SlowChess, Slow Chess Blitz)<br />\na <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant engine chess engine by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, which also comes with an own <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>. Older versions, Slow Chess 2.82a, and Slow Chess 2.96, not related to the more recent <i>Slow Chess Blitz</i>, are <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a>. \nSlow Chess is written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> with a little <a href=\"/Assembly#InlineAssembly\" title=\"Assembly\">inline assembly</a>, and was first released in July 2003. Slow Chess played the <a href=\"/ACCA_2008\" title=\"ACCA 2008\">ACCA 2008</a> operated by <a href=\"/Swaminathan_Natarajan\" title=\"Swaminathan Natarajan\">Swaminathan Natarajan</a>. After a 14-year hiatus, a new version of <b>Slow Chess Blitz</b> was released in September 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Description\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Description</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Selected_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2004\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.3dkingdoms.com/chess/slow.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"SlowChess.jpg\" src=\"/images/d/db/SlowChess.jpg\" width=\"781\" height=\"593\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>Slow Chess, <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Description\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Slow Chess 2.96's internal board is represented by a <a href=\"/10x12_Board\" title=\"10x12 Board\">10x12 board</a> in conjunction with <a href=\"/Piece-Lists\" title=\"Piece-Lists\">piece-lists</a>.\nThe <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a> applies <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a> <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">alpha-beta</a> with <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">transposition table</a> and <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">null move pruning</a> inside an <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">iterative deepening</a> framework with <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">aspiration windows</a>. \n<a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move ordering</a> is enhanced by <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">IID</a>, <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV-LVA</a>, <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">history heuristic</a>, and <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">killer heuristic</a>. Despite direct <a href=\"/Recursion\" title=\"Recursion\">recursion</a>, it does not <a href=\"/Negamax\" title=\"Negamax\">negamax</a>, but conditional min or max. \n<a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Checks</a>, <a href=\"/Recapture_Extensions\" title=\"Recapture Extensions\">recaptures</a>, <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn_Extensions\" title=\"Passed Pawn Extensions\">pawn moves to the 7th rank</a>, <a href=\"/One_Reply_Extensions\" title=\"One Reply Extensions\">single replies</a> and <a href=\"/Mate_Threat_Extensions\" title=\"Mate Threat Extensions\">mate threatening moves</a> are <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extended</a> by <a href=\"/Extensions#FractionalExtensions\" title=\"Extensions\">fractions</a> of a <a href=\"/Ply\" title=\"Ply\">ply</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n<a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a> considers <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">material</a> and <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">piece-square tables</a> with an <a href=\"/Lazy_Evaluation\" title=\"Lazy Evaluation\">lazy</a> exit if outside bounds, and otherwise cashes <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">pawn structure</a> stuff in a <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">pawn hash table</a>, evaluates <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">king safety</a> along with <a href=\"/King_Safety#KingTropism\" title=\"King Safety\">king piece tropism</a>, and various terms for <a href=\"/Evaluation_of_Pieces\" title=\"Evaluation of Pieces\">pieces</a> such as <a href=\"/Trapped_Pieces\" title=\"Trapped Pieces\">trapped bishops</a>. All evaluation <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">scores</a> greater than 4 or less than -4 are <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quantization_%28signal_processing%29\">quantized</a> and have its two least significant bits clear to make the scores multiples of ±4.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Games\">Selected Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/ACCA_2008\" title=\"ACCA 2008\">ACCA 2008</a>, round 2, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slow Chess</a> - <a href=\"/Amateur\" title=\"Amateur\">Amateur</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"ACCA 2008\"]\n[Site \"Internet Chess Club\"]\n[Date \"2008.11.08\"]\n[Round \"2\"]\n[White \"Slow Chess\"]\n[Black \"Amateur\"]\n[Result \"1-0\"]\n\n1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 e6 3.g3 d5 4.Nf3 dxc4 5.Qa4+ Bd7 6.Qxc4 Bc6 7.Bg2 Bd5 8.Qd3 Be4 9.Qd1 Nc6 \n10.O-O Nb4 11.Nc3 Bc2 12.Qd2 Ne4 13.Qe1 Nd5 14.Ne5 Bb4 15.Bd2 Bxc3 16.bxc3 f6 17.Rc1 Nxd2 \n18.Qxd2 Bf5 19.Nc4 Bg4 20.Na5 b5 21.c4 bxc4 22.Rxc4 O-O 23.Rfc1 Bh5 24.R4c5 f5 25.Nc6 Qf6 \n26.Bxd5 exd5 27.Ne5 f4 28.Nd7 Qe6 29.Nxf8 Rxf8 30.f3 fxg3 31.hxg3 Qh3 32.Qe1 Qe6 33.R5xc7 \nRe8 34.Qd2 h6 35.R1c6 Qxe2 36.Qxe2 Rxe2 37.Rxa7 Bxf3 38.Rg6 Be4 39.Rgxg7+ Kh8 40.Rge7 Rg2+ \n41.Kf1 Rxg3 42.Ra8+ Rg8 43.Rxg8+ Kxg8 44.Rxe4 dxe4 45.a4 Kf7 46.a5 1-0\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004\">2004</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2004\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=345786\">My Pick for Strongest Amateur Program (\"SlowChess!) Commercial?</a> by Nolan Denson, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 30, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=397314\">SlowChess Blitz rocks&#160;!!</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Axel_Schumacher&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Axel Schumacher (page does not exist)\">Axel Schumacher</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 22, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=397390\">SlowChess Blitz 2004</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karl-Heinz_S%C3%B6ntges&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karl-Heinz Söntges (page does not exist)\">Karl-Heinz Söntges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 23, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=397523\">More great SlowChess Blitz results!</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Axel_Schumacher&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Axel Schumacher (page does not exist)\">Axel Schumacher</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 24, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=397717\">CM9000 Default v SlowChess G-10 20-game match</a> by <a href=\"/John_Merlino\" title=\"John Merlino\">John Merlino</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=457528\">SlowChess Blitz WV is stunning is test suites!</a> by <a href=\"/Jouni_Uski\" title=\"Jouni Uski\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 24, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18458\">Slowchess 2.96 Windows 64-bit build available</a> by <a href=\"/Jim_Ablett\" title=\"Jim Ablett\">Jim Ablett</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 19, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24831\">SlowChess in ACCA</a> by <a href=\"/Swaminathan_Natarajan\" title=\"Swaminathan Natarajan\">Swaminathan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 11, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/ACCA_2008\" title=\"ACCA 2008\">ACCA 2008</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46052\">SlowChess 2.96 LS (Limit Strength)</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alexander_Schmidt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alexander Schmidt (page does not exist)\">Alexander Schmidt</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=47726\">I Am Lost With This SlowChess 2.960-Makes No Sense</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=George_Speight&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"George Speight (page does not exist)\">George Speight</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 08, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57518\">Slow Chess</a> by <a href=\"/Fernando_Villegas\" title=\"Fernando Villegas\">Fernando Villegas</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 05, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71721\">Slow Chess Blitz Classic</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 04, 2019 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420\">SlowChess Blitz Classic 2.0</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 20, 2020</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420&amp;start=42\">Re: SlowChess Blitz Classic 2.0</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2020</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74066\">Just found a 55 elo bug in SlowChess 2.1</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74184\">Learning/Tuning in SlowChess Blitz Classic</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75190\">First success with neural nets</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 23, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420&amp;start=55\">Re: SlowChess Blitz Classic 2.0</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 02, 2020&#160;» <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">SlowChess</a> 2.4</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76263\">More experiments with neural nets</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420&amp;start=73\">Re: SlowChess Blitz Classic 2.0</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2021&#160;» <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">SlowChess</a> 2.5</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77492\">Some more experiments with neural nets</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420&amp;start=94\">SlowChess Blitz Classic 2.6</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 20, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420&amp;start=109\">SlowChess Blitz 2.7</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73420&amp;start=129\">SlowChess Blitz Classic 2.8</a> by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.3dkingdoms.com/chess/slow.htm\">Slow Chess Blitz, a free chess program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.3dkingdoms.com/chess/implementation.htm\">Programming Details - Slow Chess | Extensions Used, Detailed Description</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.3dkingdoms.com/chess/learning.html\">Automatic Tuning &amp; Learning for Slow Chess Blitz Classic</a> by by <a href=\"/Jonathan_Kreuzer\" title=\"Jonathan Kreuzer\">Jonathan Kreuzer</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.3dkingdoms.com/chess/history.htm\">History of Slow Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Slow%20Chess&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Slow Chess Blitz</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/15</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Slow_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editse